760
00:43:56,831 --> 00:43:57,861
Excuse me.

761
00:44:02,271 --> 00:44:04,601
(2026
Fall 3H Acupressure Bed Briefing)

762
00:44:04,741 --> 00:44:05,841
This is nice.

763
00:44:06,501 --> 00:44:09,171
- Really?
- Now you've tried it, how is it?

764
00:44:10,611 --> 00:44:13,811
- My body feels looser. Refreshing.
- Right?

765
00:44:13,911 --> 00:44:14,951
Yes.

766
00:44:14,951 --> 00:44:17,751
Attendees, shall we move
to the briefing venue now?

767
00:44:17,811 --> 00:44:19,381
- Yes.
- Yes.

768
00:44:23,821 --> 00:44:28,131
(2026
Fall 3H Acupressure Bed Briefing)

769
00:44:28,361 --> 00:44:30,261
You can have a seat here.

770
00:44:31,761 --> 00:44:35,071
Okay, could you take my picture
here? Got it?

771
00:44:35,801 --> 00:44:36,871
Got it.

772
00:44:37,901 --> 00:44:41,071
(2026
Fall 3H Acupressure Bed Briefing)

773
00:44:41,141 --> 00:44:45,241
I've always been very interested
in health,

774
00:44:45,311 --> 00:44:47,611
and in running this center myself,

775
00:44:47,841 --> 00:44:50,951
I've found that more people
than I thought...

776
00:44:51,051 --> 00:44:52,781
are very interested
in living a healthy life.

777
00:44:53,381 --> 00:44:57,051
We have conducted countless studies
to address their concerns.

778
00:44:57,421 --> 00:44:58,721
Since you have all had a chance...

779
00:44:58,791 --> 00:45:00,391
to fully experience
our product today,

780
00:45:00,661 --> 00:45:02,831
if you are interested
in running a center,

781
00:45:02,891 --> 00:45:04,701
please feel free to ask us anytime.

782
00:45:05,631 --> 00:45:09,271
Excuse me. I've been looking
into the health business,

783
00:45:09,601 --> 00:45:12,571
and experiencing it firsthand
really helps me understand.

784
00:45:12,641 --> 00:45:14,171
Thank you so much.

785
00:45:15,411 --> 00:45:17,311
Now, for our next segment,

786
00:45:17,711 --> 00:45:20,841
we have our special guest
for today's event,

787
00:45:21,581 --> 00:45:23,411
Dr. Han Seong Mi.

788
00:45:23,551 --> 00:45:27,351
We will hear from her on how to
manage our minds for a healthy life.

789
00:45:30,851 --> 00:45:32,021
Dr. Han, come on up.

790
00:45:32,221 --> 00:45:34,861
What is this all of a sudden?
I am not prepared.

791
00:45:34,961 --> 00:45:37,491
I got all the intel from Ju Ah.

792
00:45:37,591 --> 00:45:38,761
I heard
you're such an expert speaker,

793
00:45:38,831 --> 00:45:40,161
you can give a speech
at a moment's notice.

794
00:45:40,961 --> 00:45:43,401
Hurry, come on.

795
00:45:43,671 --> 00:45:48,811
(2026
Fall 3H Acupressure Bed Briefing)

796
00:45:49,841 --> 00:45:51,281
Hello, everyone.

797
00:45:52,381 --> 00:45:55,151
- I am Han Seong Mi.
- Go, Han Seong Mi.

798
00:45:55,981 --> 00:45:57,351
So cool.

799
00:45:58,521 --> 00:46:00,681
It has been a while
since I have stood...

800
00:46:00,751 --> 00:46:02,291
in front of so many people,

801
00:46:02,991 --> 00:46:04,251
so I am a little nervous.

802
00:46:04,891 --> 00:46:05,891
Excuse me, Dr. Han,

803
00:46:05,961 --> 00:46:07,991
please say your signature line
for us.

804
00:46:08,261 --> 00:46:12,061
- Please do it. Quickly, please.
- Do it. Let us hear it.

805
00:46:12,131 --> 00:46:13,131
Let us hear it.

806
00:46:16,071 --> 00:46:18,541
To everyone here today,

807
00:46:19,471 --> 00:46:22,441
I prescribe a recipe for love.

808
00:46:23,811 --> 00:46:26,241
- I'm so touched. So touched.
- I know, right?

809
00:46:26,311 --> 00:46:27,311
That's so moving.

810
00:46:29,051 --> 00:46:34,051
I have always told my patients
to take good care of their minds,

811
00:46:35,191 --> 00:46:37,721
but now that I have become
a cancer patient myself,

812
00:46:38,491 --> 00:46:40,261
I realize how difficult that is.

813
00:46:42,061 --> 00:46:44,961
Because I did not
want to worry anyone,

814
00:46:45,431 --> 00:46:47,001
I smiled and endured it all alone.

815
00:46:48,701 --> 00:46:50,231
Then I realized something.

816
00:46:51,171 --> 00:46:53,101
Pain only grows bigger...

817
00:46:53,171 --> 00:46:56,611
the more you hide it
and bear it alone.

818
00:46:57,611 --> 00:46:58,611
Everyone,

819
00:46:59,111 --> 00:47:00,811
when you are struggling
and exhausted,

820
00:47:01,281 --> 00:47:05,451
do not try to endure it alone.
Look at the people around you.

821
00:47:06,521 --> 00:47:08,421
When you find
the courage to be loved,

822
00:47:09,251 --> 00:47:11,391
that is when healing begins.

823
00:47:20,661 --> 00:47:22,101
Ta-da.

824
00:47:22,671 --> 00:47:25,241
All right, everyone.
For the next 30 minutes,

825
00:47:25,371 --> 00:47:27,371
