a fan signing event...

826
00:47:27,441 --> 00:47:29,971
- with Dr. Han Seong Mi.
- Oh my goodness. Quick.

827
00:47:30,341 --> 00:47:31,581
- Get her autograph quickly.
- Hurry up, quick.

828
00:47:31,641 --> 00:47:32,641
This way.

829
00:47:33,311 --> 00:47:37,111
Please form a single line.
All right, get in line.

830
00:47:37,751 --> 00:47:39,981
- I'm Kim Ji Hye.
- Oh, yes. Kim Ji Hye.

831
00:47:40,051 --> 00:47:41,051
Yes.

832
00:47:48,261 --> 00:47:49,931
- Thank you. Yes.
- Hello.

833
00:47:49,991 --> 00:47:50,991
And your name is?

834
00:47:51,831 --> 00:47:54,931
- Oh, you want me to sign it here?
- Yes. Joo Ji Ha...

835
00:47:55,531 --> 00:47:57,771
Joo Ji Ha...

836
00:47:59,341 --> 00:48:02,071
Dr. Han. You must be thirsty.

837
00:48:02,141 --> 00:48:04,511
Have a sip of this.
It's chamomile tea.

838
00:48:10,581 --> 00:48:13,721
You see?
People haven't forgotten you at all.

839
00:48:13,921 --> 00:48:16,551
So get well soon
and make your comeback. All right?

840
00:48:17,451 --> 00:48:21,061
- Thank you.
- Don't thank me. I thank you.

841
00:48:21,461 --> 00:48:22,931
I got to look so cool today.

842
00:48:32,741 --> 00:48:34,041
Hello.

843
00:48:34,971 --> 00:48:35,971
Well, hello there.

844
00:48:36,041 --> 00:48:39,411
The men were supposed to have drinks
at my place today,

845
00:48:39,481 --> 00:48:42,511
