849
00:48:51,151 --> 00:48:54,121
Oh my goodness, Se Ri.

850
00:48:54,991 --> 00:48:57,291
Oh my, what's with the face mask?

851
00:48:57,691 --> 00:48:58,731
Well...

852
00:48:59,131 --> 00:49:00,531
Oh dear.

853
00:49:00,831 --> 00:49:03,601
Oh my,
what brings you here at this hour?

854
00:49:03,771 --> 00:49:07,101
Well, I just brought over some food.

855
00:49:07,641 --> 00:49:09,971
Would you like to just leave it?

856
00:49:10,041 --> 00:49:12,611
We're like this. I'm so embarrassed.

857
00:49:14,741 --> 00:49:15,811
What? Why?

858
00:49:16,051 --> 00:49:20,151
I'm jealous. I want to join you.

859
00:49:20,851 --> 00:49:25,421
- What? You are?
- Come on. Just go. Quick.

860
00:49:26,391 --> 00:49:27,821
Come on in. Join us.

861
00:49:28,461 --> 00:49:29,491
Really?

862
00:49:29,831 --> 00:49:31,961
Come on in.
We have plenty of face masks.

863
00:49:32,401 --> 00:49:34,101
- That's right. Come in.
- Come on in.

864
00:49:35,031 --> 00:49:37,901
