- Okay.

867
00:49:48,081 --> 00:49:50,751
All right, don't drink too much.

868
00:49:50,851 --> 00:49:53,121
- Yes, sir.
- Okay.

869
00:49:54,281 --> 00:49:56,351
Do not worry about things here.
Just go have fun.

870
00:49:56,591 --> 00:49:59,061
- Yes, Father. Yes.
- Yes.

871
00:50:00,621 --> 00:50:05,001
- Well, son-in-law. Congratulations.
- Thank you.

872
00:50:08,061 --> 00:50:10,671
All right,
then let me pour you a drink too.

873
00:50:11,031 --> 00:50:13,941
- Yes. All right.
- Thanks for letting Ji Hu go.

874
00:50:14,401 --> 00:50:17,541
That was Ju Ah's decision.

875
00:50:18,911 --> 00:50:20,841
You're amazing, Yang Hyun Bin.

876
00:50:21,011 --> 00:50:22,051
Oh man, look at this.

877
00:50:22,151 --> 00:50:24,111
We have
another devoted husband here.

878
00:50:24,181 --> 00:50:25,221
Father, are you jealous?

879
00:50:25,881 --> 00:50:26,921
