- Hang up. Call me back later.
- Ju Ah. I love you.

902
00:51:30,351 --> 00:51:33,951
- Ju Ah, I miss you.
- Gosh, what is with him?

903
00:51:34,021 --> 00:51:36,991
- Is that really Hyun Bin's voice?
- Yes, it is.

904
00:51:36,991 --> 00:51:40,991
- He's drunk. He's drunk.
- Gong Ju Ah, I love you!

905
00:51:47,661 --> 00:51:48,971
Dong Suk!

906
00:51:49,601 --> 00:51:52,771
My endorphin. I love you!

907
00:51:55,271 --> 00:51:59,041
- My vitamin. I love you too.
- Goodness.

908
00:51:59,641 --> 00:52:00,711
What's wrong with it?

909
00:52:01,781 --> 00:52:02,911
Hey, hey. Give me that.

910
00:52:03,651 --> 00:52:04,651
Seong Mi!

911
00:52:05,151 --> 00:52:06,781
I love you more!

912
00:52:07,051 --> 00:52:10,121
I love you to the moon and back.

913
00:52:10,121 --> 00:52:11,661
