914
00:52:11,661 --> 00:52:13,591
- Your turn, Mom. Quick.
- No!

915
00:52:13,691 --> 00:52:16,831
- Go on.
- You too, Dr. Han. Hurry.

916
00:52:18,661 --> 00:52:20,031
Me too.

917
00:52:25,541 --> 00:52:27,771
Me too?

918
00:52:29,111 --> 00:52:31,211
Se Ri!
I love you as much as the universe,

919
00:52:31,211 --> 00:52:33,081
