920
00:52:33,581 --> 00:52:34,581
Oh, my. Honestly.

921
00:52:34,641 --> 00:52:38,481
Oh my, I love you too,
Dr. Yang. That's enough now.

922
00:52:38,621 --> 00:52:39,751
Gosh, I'm next.

923
00:52:39,821 --> 00:52:41,021
- I really love you.
- What is with everyone?

924
00:52:41,051 --> 00:52:42,291
- Me first.
- Hey.

925
00:52:42,491 --> 00:52:44,221
- Gong Ju Ah.
- Se Ri, take all my money.

926
00:52:44,291 --> 00:52:45,691
- Dong Suk.
- Ju Ah.

927
00:52:45,761 --> 00:52:47,821
- All my assets are yours.
- Dong Suk.

928
00:52:47,891 --> 00:52:49,691
- Hey, hang up. Quickly.
- Hey, hang up.

929
00:52:50,391 --> 00:52:52,701
- My gosh.
- Oh my.

930
00:52:53,761 --> 00:52:54,831
