940
00:53:17,991 --> 00:53:18,991
Yes.

941
00:53:20,391 --> 00:53:21,691
Hello.

942
00:53:22,161 --> 00:53:24,661
Hello. It's so beautiful.

943
00:53:24,731 --> 00:53:26,031
