Hey, you can't walk there.

945
00:53:28,131 --> 00:53:30,071
Come on, two at a time.

946
00:53:30,401 --> 00:53:33,071
Put your things down first.
And Seong Min, you'll be over there.

947
00:53:33,201 --> 00:53:34,741
