949
00:53:40,241 --> 00:53:41,711
- You're here.
- Oh dear.

950
00:53:42,611 --> 00:53:43,851
- Father, you're here?
- Oh.

951
00:53:43,911 --> 00:53:44,911
You're here.

952
00:53:45,351 --> 00:53:47,551
- Hey.
- Father.

953
00:53:47,851 --> 00:53:48,991
- You're here.
- Father.

954
00:53:49,521 --> 00:53:51,821
- You're here?
- Father.

955
00:53:52,561 --> 00:53:55,591
- Grandfather, was your trip good?
- Of course.

956
00:53:55,891 --> 00:53:58,391
