you've lost some weight.

958
00:54:02,071 --> 00:54:03,071
What?

959
00:54:03,931 --> 00:54:07,871
- Father, must've traveled all over.
- Yes, I did.

960
00:54:08,771 --> 00:54:10,871
So, any baby news from you two yet?

961
00:54:11,371 --> 00:54:13,581
Father, you just got here.

962
00:54:16,951 --> 00:54:20,051
Dr. Han, Mother,
we should go see the bride.

963
00:54:20,151 --> 00:54:23,191
- Yes. Mother, let's go.
- Yes, over there.

964
00:54:26,821 --> 00:54:30,061
- Eun Bin, let's go inside too.
- Okay, let's go.

965
00:54:35,231 --> 00:54:37,471
- Good to see you.
- Yes, the day has finally come.

966
00:54:38,071 --> 00:54:39,071
Jeong Han.

967
00:54:42,941 --> 00:54:44,071
